Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:12.46,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}在满是人影的街道尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.74,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}有你在那里
