Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:34.35,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:38.84,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}赐予了我光芒
